          "date": "2025-04-27 17:15:13.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-18813 osd-wbcfs: fix coverity warnings",
        "message": "LU-18813 osd-wbcfs: fix coverity warnings\n\nosd_mksym() is not implemented yet, so remove the dead code.\n\nThe CDEBUG() in osd_index_dir_insert() can incorrectly\ndereference a NULL dentry. Also, it accesses d_flags without\nholding a lock. Move the CDEBUG() after out_dput and remove\nthe d_flags access (rather than do expensive locking).\n\nCoverityID: 463351 (\"Data race condition\")\nCoverityID: 463341 (\"Structurally dead code\")\nCoverityID: 463344 (\"Dereference after null check\")\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity fstype=wbcfs mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 osscount=4 ostcount=1\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Ia8a8f223e3cf8339f4326e86c43389f0e60cfb05\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
